#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:54
msgid "Key Components for Implementation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:56
msgid ""
"To add support for a new diffusion model, you will need to define or "
"configure the following components:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:58
msgid ""
"**`PipelineConfig`**: A dataclass holding static configurations for your "
"model pipeline — precision settings, model architecture parameters, and "
"callback methods used by the standard `DenoisingStage` and `DecodingStage`. "
"Each model has its own subclass."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:60
msgid ""
"**`SamplingParams`**: A dataclass defining runtime generation parameters — "
"`prompt`, `negative_prompt`, `guidance_scale`, `num_inference_steps`, "
"`seed`, `height`, `width`, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:62
msgid ""
"**Pre-processing stage(s)**: Either a single model-specific `{Model}"
"BeforeDenoisingStage` (Hybrid style) or a combination of standard stages "
"(Modular style). See [Two Pipeline Styles](#two-pipeline-styles) above."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:64
msgid ""
"**`ComposedPipeline`**: A class that wires together your pre-processing "
"stage(s) with the standard `DenoisingStage` and `DecodingStage`. See base "
"definitions:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:65
msgid ""
"[`ComposedPipelineBase`](https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang/blob/main/"
"python/sglang/multimodal_gen/runtime/pipelines_core/composed_pipeline_base."
"py)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:66
msgid ""
"[`PipelineStage`](https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang/blob/main/python/"
"sglang/multimodal_gen/runtime/pipelines_core/stages/base.py)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:67
msgid ""
"[Central registry](https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang/blob/main/python/"
"sglang/multimodal_gen/registry.py)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:69
msgid ""
"**Modules (model components)**: Each pipeline references modules loaded from "
"the model repository (e.g., Diffusers `model_index.json`):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:70
msgid "`text_encoder`: Encodes text prompts into embeddings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:71
msgid "`tokenizer`: Tokenizes raw text input for the text encoder(s)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:72
msgid ""
"`processor`: Preprocesses images and extracts features; often used in image-"
"to-image tasks."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:73
msgid "`image_encoder`: Specialized image feature extractor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:74
msgid ""
"`dit/transformer`: The core denoising network (DiT/UNet architecture) "
"operating in latent space."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:75
msgid "`scheduler`: Controls the timestep schedule and denoising dynamics."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/support_new_models.md:76
msgid ""
"`vae`: Variational Autoencoder for encoding/decoding between pixel space and "
"latent space."
msgstr ""

